rows.label: qst005603_msg001
rows.name: Hi there!

rows.label: qst005603_msg002
rows.name:
What you people want?
After something in particular?

rows.label: qst005603_msg003
rows.name:
We're investigating a certain
ancient tablet.

rows.label: qst005603_msg004
rows.name: Ancient tablet?

rows.label: qst005603_msg005
rows.name:
Yep. It's transparent, really thin,
and floats in the air.

rows.label: qst005603_msg006
rows.name: Hmmm... Sound very unusual.

rows.label: qst005603_msg007
rows.name:
Me has heard of ancient technology
to make words and pictures float in air.

rows.label: qst005603_msg008
rows.name:
Maybe this tablet related to
that technology.

rows.label: qst005603_msg009
rows.name:
We heard you might have an ancient
tome related to that tablet. Is it true?

rows.label: qst005603_msg010
rows.name: Me does have tome from that era.

rows.label: qst005603_msg011
rows.name:
Might contain information about
strange tablet.

rows.label: qst005603_msg012
rows.name: Friends want to read tome?

rows.label: qst005603_msg013
rows.name: Really? You'd let us?!

rows.label: qst005603_msg014
rows.name:
Yes yes. Friends need to decipher
tome by selves, though.

rows.label: qst005603_msg015
rows.name: How was it, Shiki?

rows.label: qst005603_msg016
rows.name:
It did seem like the text was about
the right kind of ancient technology.

rows.label: qst005603_msg017
rows.name:
But there wasn't much about that
tablet in particular...

rows.label: qst005603_msg018
rows.name:
All I could find was a weird name
that said "E46S"...

rows.label: qst005603_msg019
rows.name: You don't think that's...

rows.label: qst005603_msg020
rows.name:
Of course! It must be part of
the twelve-character code!

rows.label: qst005603_msg021
rows.name:
Why the tome can't just list the
whole code in one go, I don't know...
But at least it's progress.

rows.label: qst005603_msg022
rows.name: Yep! It's all thanks to you guys!
